name: kvin-nb1
docker_compose_file:
services:
  jupyter:
    image: quay.io/jupyter/base-notebook
    user: root
    network_mode: host
    privileged: true
    environment:
      - GRANT_SUDO=yes
    ports:
      - "80:8888"
    volumes:
      - /:/host/
      - /var/run/tappd.sock:/var/run/tappd.sock
